java.lang.Cloneable
public final class SvgDimension
extends SvgEntityReference

This class encapsulates Dxf Dimension. Any Dimension reference will be translated into a <use> xml link reference in Svg that references a <symbol> in the SVG preamble.

0.01 - February 26, 2003
